0.6.0 - uses inet_pton to verify addresses
0.5.8 - increases buffer to 8192 bytes from 4096
0.5.7 - adds windows server thread return code, removes _exit on thread errors
0.5.6 - displays text for windows socket errors, creates detached tunnel_thread
0.5.5 - windows uses 3 threads per tunnel, unix still uses 1
0.5.4 - server responds with ready, fail, addr, auth to indicate tunnel failure
0.5.3 - process_tunnel returns on socket errors to close out thread
0.5.2 - windows host can now lookup cid by name
0.5.1 - supports duplicate vm names
0.5.0 - adds windows service functionality
0.4.1 - corrects short time on select changed from 100 usec to 1 sec to reduce resources
0.4.0 - outputs pid on listen message
0.3.0 - attempts to restrict dest ips
0.2.6 - cleans vmci/virtio and host/client logic
0.2.5 - windows process_tunnel improvements
0.2.4 - tries af 36 if 40 fails on linux
0.2.3 - flushes stdout before daemonize
0.2.1 - now daemonizes server mode

